{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"This is my niece, Stella."},{"time":3561,"text":"She's just turned one and started to walk."},{"time":6057,"text":"And she's walking in that really cool way that\none-year-olds do,"},{"time":9057,"text":"a kind of teetering, my-body's-moving-\ntoo-fast-for-my-legs kind of way."},{"time":14273,"text":"It is absolutely gorgeous."},{"time":16762,"text":"And one of her favorite \nthings to do at the moment"},{"time":19380,"text":"is to stare at herself in the mirror."},{"time":21844,"text":"She absolutely loves her reflection."},{"time":24999,"text":"She giggles and squeals, and gives\nherself these big, wet kisses."},{"time":31371,"text":"It is beautiful."},{"time":33384,"text":"Apparently, all of her friends do this and my mom\ntells me that I used to do this,"},{"time":38676,"text":"and it got me thinking:"},{"time":40191,"text":"When did I stop doing this?"},{"time":43648,"text":"When is it suddenly not okay to love \nthe way that we look?"},{"time":48951,"text":"Because apparently we don't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51636,"text":"Ten thousand people every month google,"},{"time":55065,"text":"\"Am I ugly?\""},{"time":57211,"text":"This is Faye. Faye is 13 and she \nlives in Denver."},{"time":61734,"text":"And like any teenager, she just wants to \nbe liked and to fit in."},{"time":65708,"text":"It's Sunday night."},{"time":67517,"text":"She's getting ready for the week ahead at school."},{"time":70211,"text":"And she's slightly dreading it, and \nshe's a bit confused because"},{"time":72497,"text":"despite her mom telling her all the time"},{"time":75106,"text":"that she's beautiful,"},{"time":77452,"text":"every day at school, someone tells her \nthat she's ugly."},{"time":83364,"text":"Because of the difference between what her mom \ntells her and what her friends"},{"time":86629,"text":"at school, or her peers at school are telling her,"},{"time":89653,"text":"she doesn't know who to believe."},{"time":92018,"text":"So, she takes a video of herself. \nShe posts it to YouTube"},{"time":95967,"text":"and she asks people to please leave \na comment:"},{"time":98293,"text":"\"Am I pretty or am I ugly?\""},{"time":100410,"text":"Well, so far, Faye has received \nover 13,000 comments."},{"time":105415,"text":"Some of them are so nasty, they don't \nbear thinking about."},{"time":109019,"text":"This is an average, healthy-looking \nteenage girl receiving this feedback"},{"time":114950,"text":"at one of the most emotionally vulnerable\ntimes in her life."},{"time":119184,"text":"Thousands of people are posting videos like this,"},{"time":123081,"text":"mostly teenage girls, reaching out in this way."},{"time":126918,"text":"But what's leading them to do this?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":128867,"text":"Well, today's teenagers are rarely alone."},{"time":132774,"text":"They're under pressure to be online\nand available at all times,"},{"time":137604,"text":"talking, messaging, liking, commenting, \nsharing, posting —"},{"time":142145,"text":"it never ends."},{"time":144062,"text":"Never before have we been so connected,"},{"time":147012,"text":"so continuously, so instantaneously, so young."},{"time":151772,"text":"And as one mom told me, it's like there's a party\nin their bedroom every night."},{"time":156632,"text":"There's simply no privacy."},{"time":160071,"text":"And the social pressures that go along \nwith that are relentless."},{"time":164424,"text":"This always-on environment is training\nour kids to value themselves"},{"time":169302,"text":"based on the number of likes they get"},{"time":171013,"text":"and the types of comments that they receive."},{"time":174012,"text":"There's no separation between online and offline life."},{"time":178591,"text":"What's real or what isn't is really\nhard to tell the difference between."},{"time":184164,"text":"And it's also really hard to tell the difference \nbetween what's authentic"},{"time":187955,"text":"and what's digitally manipulated."},{"time":190241,"text":"What's a highlight in someone's life versus\nwhat's normal in the context of everyday."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195886,"text":"And where are they looking to for inspiration?"},{"time":199017,"text":"Well, you can see the kinds of images\nthat are covering the newsfeeds"},{"time":202829,"text":"of girls today."},{"time":204441,"text":"Size zero models still dominate our catwalks."},{"time":207655,"text":"Airbrushing is now routine."},{"time":210312,"text":"And trends like #thinspiration, #thighgap,"},{"time":212923,"text":"#bikinibridge and #proana."},{"time":215042,"text":"For those who don't know, #proana means pro-anorexia."},{"time":218586,"text":"These trends are teamed with the \nstereotyping and flagrant objectification"},{"time":223427,"text":"of women in today's popular culture."},{"time":225631,"text":"It is not hard to see what girls are\nbenchmarking themselves against."},{"time":231608,"text":"But boys are not immune to this either."},{"time":234057,"text":"Aspiring to the chiseled jaw lines and ripped six packs\nof superhero-like sports stars"},{"time":239189,"text":"and playboy music artists."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241707,"text":"But, what's the problem with all of this?"},{"time":244079,"text":"Well, surely we want our kids to grow up as healthy, \nwell balanced individuals."},{"time":251132,"text":"But in an image-obsessed culture, we are\ntraining our kids"},{"time":255008,"text":"to spend more time and mental effort on \ntheir appearance"},{"time":259816,"text":"at the expense of all of the other aspects\nof their identities."},{"time":264111,"text":"So, things like their relationships, the development\nof their physical abilities,"},{"time":268221,"text":"and their studies and so on begin to suffer."},{"time":272256,"text":"Six out of 10 girls are now choosing not to do \nsomething because they don't"},{"time":277858,"text":"think they look good enough."},{"time":279722,"text":"These are not trivial activities."},{"time":282104,"text":"These are fundamental activities to their\ndevelopment as humans"},{"time":286008,"text":"and as contributors to society and to \nthe workforce."},{"time":291358,"text":"Thirty-one percent, nearly one in \nthree teenagers, are withdrawing"},{"time":297279,"text":"from classroom debate. They're failing"},{"time":298851,"text":"to engage in classroom debate because"},{"time":300982,"text":"they don't want to draw attention to the \nway that they look."},{"time":304232,"text":"One in five are not showing up to class at all"},{"time":307089,"text":"on days when they don't feel good about it."},{"time":309456,"text":"And when it comes to exams,"},{"time":310876,"text":"if you don't think you look good enough,"},{"time":313225,"text":"specifically if you don't think you are thin enough,"},{"time":316561,"text":"you will score a lower grade point average"},{"time":319667,"text":"than your peers who are not concerned with this."},{"time":322464,"text":"And this is consistent across Finland, the U.S."},{"time":325607,"text":"and China, and is true regardless of how much\nyou actually weigh."},{"time":331664,"text":"So to be super clear, we're talking about the"},{"time":334546,"text":"way you think you look, not how\nyou actually look."},{"time":339789,"text":"Low body confidence is undermining \nacademic achievement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344544,"text":"But it's also damaging health."},{"time":346952,"text":"Teenagers with low body confidence\ndo less physical activity,"},{"time":350534,"text":"eat less fruits and vegetables,"},{"time":352657,"text":"partake in more unhealthy weight control\npractices"},{"time":355692,"text":"that can lead to eating disorders."},{"time":358101,"text":"They have lower self-esteem."},{"time":360654,"text":"They're more easily influenced by people around them"},{"time":362740,"text":"and they're at greater risk of depression."},{"time":365488,"text":"And we think it's for all of these reasons\nthat they take more risks"},{"time":369416,"text":"with things like alcohol and drug use;"},{"time":373141,"text":"crash dieting; cosmetic surgery; \nunprotected, earlier sex;"},{"time":378552,"text":"and self-harm."},{"time":380682,"text":"The pursuit of the perfect body is putting\npressure on our healthcare systems"},{"time":384816,"text":"and costing our governments billions of \ndollars every year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":389263,"text":"And we don't grow out of it."},{"time":391916,"text":"Women who think they're overweight — again,"},{"time":394815,"text":"regardless of whether they are or are not —"},{"time":397567,"text":"have higher rates of absenteeism."},{"time":400877,"text":"Seventeen percent of women would"},{"time":402934,"text":"not show up to a job interview on"},{"time":405651,"text":"a day when they weren't feeling confident\nabout the way that they look."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410961,"text":"Have a think about what this is doing"},{"time":412866,"text":"to our economy."},{"time":414582,"text":"If we could overcome this, what that"},{"time":416444,"text":"opportunity looks like."},{"time":418754,"text":"Unlocking this potential is in the interest"},{"time":421349,"text":"of every single one of us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":424609,"text":"But how do we do that?"},{"time":426181,"text":"Well, talking, on its own, only gets you so far."},{"time":430153,"text":"It's not enough by itself."},{"time":432037,"text":"If you actually want to make a difference,"},{"time":433462,"text":"you have to do something."},{"time":435598,"text":"And we've learned there are three key ways:"},{"time":438672,"text":"The first is we have to educate for body confidence."},{"time":441314,"text":"We have to help our teenagers develop"},{"time":443236,"text":"strategies to overcome image-related pressures"},{"time":446581,"text":"and build their self-esteem."},{"time":448131,"text":"Now, the good news is that there are"},{"time":450117,"text":"many programs out there available\nto do this."},{"time":454070,"text":"The bad news is that most of them don't work."},{"time":457820,"text":"I was shocked to learn that many well-meaning"},{"time":462527,"text":"programs are inadvertently actually"},{"time":465755,"text":"making the situation worse."},{"time":469150,"text":"So we need to make damn sure that"},{"time":470856,"text":"the programs that our kids are receiving"},{"time":473459,"text":"are not only having a positive impact,"},{"time":475419,"text":"but having a lasting impact as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":478387,"text":"And the research shows \nthat the best programs"},{"time":481779,"text":"address six key areas:"},{"time":483854,"text":"The first is the influence of family, \nfriends and relationships."},{"time":487917,"text":"The second is media and celebrity culture,"},{"time":491381,"text":"then how to handle teasing and bullying,"},{"time":493433,"text":"the way we compete and compare with\none another"},{"time":495425,"text":"based on looks,"},{"time":496962,"text":"talking about appearance — some people"},{"time":498712,"text":"call this \"body talk\" or \"fat talk\" —"},{"time":501219,"text":"and finally, the foundations of respecting"},{"time":503693,"text":"and looking after yourself."},{"time":505467,"text":"These six things are crucial starting points"},{"time":507940,"text":"for anyone serious about delivering"},{"time":510831,"text":"body-confidence education that works."},{"time":513768,"text":"An education is critical,"},{"time":516074,"text":"but tackling this problem is going"},{"time":517895,"text":"to require each and everyone of us"},{"time":520665,"text":"to step up and be better role models"},{"time":523255,"text":"for the women and girls in our own lives."},{"time":526233,"text":"Challenging the status quo of how"},{"time":528166,"text":"women are seen and talked about in\nour own circles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531170,"text":"It is not okay that we judge the contribution"},{"time":535212,"text":"of our politicians by their haircuts"},{"time":538370,"text":"or the size of their breasts,"},{"time":540099,"text":"or to infer that the determination or the success"},{"time":543464,"text":"of an Olympian is down \nto her not being a looker."},{"time":546697,"text":"We need to start judging people by what they do,"},{"time":549803,"text":"not what they look like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":552354,"text":"We can all start by taking responsibility \nfor the types of pictures"},{"time":556718,"text":"and comments that we post"},{"time":558361,"text":"on our own social networks."},{"time":560548,"text":"We can compliment people based on \ntheir effort"},{"time":564777,"text":"and their actions"},{"time":566180,"text":"and not on their appearance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":568861,"text":"And let me ask you,"},{"time":570375,"text":"when was the last time that you"},{"time":571663,"text":"kissed a mirror?"},{"time":573519,"text":"Ultimately, we need to work together"},{"time":575812,"text":"as communities, as governments"},{"time":578236,"text":"and as businesses to really change\nthis culture of ours"},{"time":582701,"text":"so that our kids grow up valuing their \nwhole selves,"},{"time":587306,"text":"valuing individuality, diversity, inclusion."},{"time":591969,"text":"We need to put the people that are\nmaking a real difference"},{"time":594765,"text":"on our pedestals, making a difference"},{"time":598173,"text":"in the real world."},{"time":600153,"text":"Giving them the airtime, because only then"},{"time":602863,"text":"will we create a different world."},{"time":604728,"text":"A world where our kids are free to become"},{"time":608057,"text":"the best versions of themselves,"},{"time":611302,"text":"where the way they think they look"},{"time":613248,"text":"never holds them back from being\nwho they are"},{"time":615889,"text":"or achieving what they want in life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":618835,"text":"Think about what this might mean \nfor someone in your life."},{"time":623053,"text":"Who have you got in mind?"},{"time":624551,"text":"Is it your wife?"},{"time":625956,"text":"Your sister?"},{"time":627344,"text":"Your daughter?"},{"time":628993,"text":"Your niece?"},{"time":630266,"text":"Your friend? It could just be the woman \na couple of seats away"},{"time":633329,"text":"from you today."},{"time":634624,"text":"What would it mean for her"},{"time":637314,"text":"if she were freed from that voice"},{"time":641072,"text":"of her inner critic, nagging her to have"},{"time":644106,"text":"longer legs, thinner thighs, smaller stomach,"},{"time":646897,"text":"shorter feet?"},{"time":648332,"text":"What could it mean for her if we overcame this"},{"time":651700,"text":"and unlocked her potential in that way?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":656213,"text":"Right now, our culture's obsession"},{"time":660035,"text":"with image is holding us all back."},{"time":663390,"text":"But let's show our kids the truth."},{"time":665917,"text":"Let's show them that the way you look"},{"time":667932,"text":"is just one part of your identity"},{"time":671647,"text":"and that the truth is we love them"},{"time":674360,"text":"for who they are"},{"time":675931,"text":"and what they do"},{"time":677898,"text":"and how they make us feel."},{"time":680598,"text":"Let's build self-esteem into our school curriculums."},{"time":684683,"text":"Let's each and every one of us change the way"},{"time":687343,"text":"we talk and compare ourselves to other people."},{"time":690778,"text":"And let's work together as communities,"},{"time":693508,"text":"from grassroots to governments,"},{"time":696302,"text":"so that the happy little one-year-olds"},{"time":698477,"text":"of today become the confident"},{"time":701354,"text":"changemakers of tomorrow."},{"time":703969,"text":"Let's do this."},{"time":705986,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}